biography: Anders, a familiar name at Vihti Golf Club, is known for his strategic play and thoughtful demeanor on the course. While generally reserved, those who know Anders speak of his dry wit and his penchant for complex strategy games off the course.

Having participated in the Hector Trophée once, Anders is considered to be retired from future events. Although he will not be participating in Hector Trophée 2025, fans will remember his contributions to the camaraderie of the event.
